metadata.name: Boarding
metadata.description:
A simple fishing boat in the midst of water is enough to awaken in the mind of the beholder a sense of vastness of the sea and at the same time of peace and contentment.  
This is top down shot taken from DJI Mavic Pro when fishermen were using mini boat for boarding fishing trawler in order to start their fishing journey for the day. since this place doesn't have a dock  fishermen has to anchor their trawler at a distance from shore and they use mini boat for travel from shore to trawler and back.
